{"tid":720932,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"石詠莉日本拍MV「闖地獄」","createTime":"2018-06-28T10:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T10:50:51.000Z","uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eece75d5c5b74b1c68ea63dc95e84050d76e63bf","tid":720932,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:03:02.000Z","msg":"歌手石詠莉（Sukie）昨日為新城電台擔任嘉賓主持，前日她才由日本東京返港：「去咗四日，入行咁耐未試過地獄通告，凌晨12點休息、兩點又要起身化妝，今次係幫新碟影封套同拍MV。」老公鄧健泓隨行任導演及監製，提到近日大阪地震，她坦言有點擔心：「因為聽講除咗餘震，仲會有主震，以前去旅行都有遇過，好搖，但當地市民就好似唔太驚。」"},{"pid":"e892f3ba35ba01e58f989125bc0d9de056262910","tid":720932,"uid":150098,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"睇錯AV，我出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc52ef5a2dbc9d1efa6c66c6607ad1e211efa0a","tid":720932,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e892f3ba35ba01e58f989125bc0d9de056262910","tid":720932,"uid":150098,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"睇錯AV，我出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:05:56.000Z","msg":"same"},{"pid":"aa1af10ac5b283cbd00391c135090ba952fb9a88","tid":720932,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bc52ef5a2dbc9d1efa6c66c6607ad1e211efa0a","tid":720932,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e892f3ba35ba01e58f989125bc0d9de056262910","tid":720932,"uid":150098,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"睇錯AV，我出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:05:56.000Z","msg":"same"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"仲要係水地獄"},{"pid":"6bf71fd03c302eb50b19c2ff18a214c4991c30fc","tid":720932,"uid":9104,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:06:31.000Z","msg":"石原莉奈日本拍AV「水地獄」"},{"pid":"14d90867de26c50bcf229dea20